dismissalText.commentary: Rachin Ravindra c Pathirana b Thushara 1 (4b 0x4 0x6) SR: 25

dismissalComment.html: top-edged to mid-on! Ravindra won't be going big tonight. Good ball, 141kph and kicking up from back of a length, it's on Ravindra before he can get through his attempted pull. Nearly drops short of Pathirana but he holds a tumbling catch going to his right
